! MTBF

<<<
Mean time between failure
<<<


$$
\frac{\text{Total elapsed time - Sum of downtime}}{\text{Total no. of failures}}
$$

! MTTR

<<<
Mean time to recover
<<<


$$
\frac{\text{Total maintenance time}}{\text{Total no. of repairs}}
$$